OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of killing boy,
OL,4,C16, with 'ninja-style' sword
OL,6,FA teenager has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fkilling a 16-year-old boy with a
OL,8,F"ninja-style" red sword bought online.
OL,10,FThe 17-year-old boy, who cannot be
OL,11,Fnamed for legal reasons, stabbed
OL,12,FRahaan Ahmed Amin in the chest on July
OL,13,F9 in retribution for an earlier
OL,14,Fstabbing, jurors heard.
OL,16,FOn Friday, the defendant was found
OL,17,Fguilty of murder and having a blade
OL,18,Ffollowing a trial at the Old Bailey.
