OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of killing boy,
OL,4,C16, with 'ninja-style' sword
OL,6,FProsecutor Kate Lumsdon KC had told
OL,7,Fjurors how the defendant had cycled
OL,8,Finto West Ham Park in Newham, east
OL,9,FLondon, with his face covered.
OL,11,FHe had produced a long red knife and
OL,12,Fattacked Rahaan before making off.
OL,14,FRahaan and his attacker were said to
OL,15,Fbe standing "toe-to-toe" before the
OL,16,Fknife was used, while another witness
OL,17,Fsaid he saw a boy coming towards him
OL,18,Fwith his hands over his chest shouting
OL,19,F"save me, save me please".
