OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of killing boy,
OL,4,C16, with 'ninja-style' sword
OL,6,FParamedics were called to the scene
OL,7,Fand Rahaan was taken to hospital where
OL,8,Fhe died the next day.
OL,10,FPolice recovered the murder weapon
OL,11,Fbearing the defendant's fingerprints
OL,12,Fand the victim's blood on the blade
OL,13,Fhanging in a tree in the park.
OL,15,FThey also uncovered a Snapchat
OL,16,Fphotograph of nine knives lined up on
OL,17,Fthe defendant's bed, one of which
OL,18,Flooked like the red sword used in the
OL,19,Fkilling.
