OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of killing boy,
OL,4,C16, with 'ninja-style' sword
OL,6,FAn identical knife had been ordered on
OL,7,Fthe internet through an online shop in
OL,8,Fthe weeks before the killing, on June
OL,9,F12.
OL,11,FThree orders had been made with a
OL,12,Fpassport belonging to the father of
OL,13,Fone of the defendant's friends who
OL,14,Ftold police he had no knowledge of the
OL,15,Fpurchase, the court heard.
OL,17,FThe last order was made with the
OL,18,Fdefendant's home as the delivery
OL,19,Faddress.
