OL,6,FJurors were told that the killing came
OL,7,Famid tensions between the defendant
OL,8,Fand victim's groups of friends.
OL,10,FWhen one of the defendant's friends
OL,11,Fwas stabbed, Rahaan had been arrested
OL,12,Fon suspicion of involvement.
OL,14,FSnapchat messages suggested the
OL,15,Fdefendant and his friends wanted to
OL,16,Fharm Rahaan in retaliation, the court
OL,17,Fwas told.
OL,19,FGiving evidence in his trial, the
OL,20,Fdefendant claimed he used the knife in
OL,21,Fself-defence.
